body:
This texture pack adds several musical instruments to your game. These tools dilute all sorts of role-playing players. The musical instruments themselves can be obtained by renaming items such as axes, swords, and so on in the anvil. The list of instruments and how to adopt them: (It is recommended to use an axe as an item for renaming)

Piano - piano ; 
classic guitar - guitar ; 
electro guitar(red) - eleguitar ; 
electro guitar(blue) - blueeleguitar ; 
bass guitar - bass ; 
drums - drum ; 

in the near future, I'm going to supplement the resource pack if at least someone likes the project.
